{"tid":246303,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［請教］泊S位點睇45度","createTime":"2017-05-17T01:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:58:17.000Z","uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb40c316bdb4cbc55b10a99f3acd388fe4d2fdbd","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"師父叫我feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3823ae539643343fe63edfeb24153573d19bf1","tid":246303,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"唔洗理咩度角  你首先要睇鏡 同扭軚既原理 點扭 架車會點 去做每一個扭既動作  當然你要確保個位係架車有足夠長度泊啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係下下街邊既位 長度都一樣."},{"pid":"eec2e2168e840031ade976fd32fa74d4351e0a13","tid":246303,"uid":93526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"上youtube 睇教學<br />\n有啲人會同前車平排<br />\n之后落后波 當司機位望到前車后座就扭哂入前車既方向<br />\n但記住兩車之間既距離最少要有一個人既身位"},{"pid":"18c4b13c9c28286c60a719ca21a9061f84f7ba2c","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"因為我要應付考試先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以未有街泊同前後車煩惱<br />\n得雪糕筒同白線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6df7fc9e15b692b92ce1533988b1082a9926514","tid":246303,"uid":20258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上youtube 睇教學<br />\n有啲人會同前車平排<br />\n之<span style=\"color: red;\">后</span>落<span style=\"color: red;\">后</span>波 當司機位望到前車后座就扭哂入前車既方向<br />\n但記住兩車之間既距離最少要有一個人既身位</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c033ac532702654e4929d34366a39ea38029e65","tid":246303,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"師傅教<br />\n譬如你泊你右面s位<br />\n間車係個空位前面間車，你間車pat pat同佢pat pat成一直線<br />\n跟住扭盡右面，留位左鏡<br />\n當你左鏡睇到哂空位後面架車成個車頭，就回直架車<br />\n當架車左尾轆入左泊車個位後<br />\n向左扭盡，直至架車入哂個車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdc449da1b1ee85d049ddb3c555b0056cccf45b","tid":246303,"uid":12683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92ad87ee65ea89eda1e1d819d5eb253489871cc","tid":246303,"uid":19977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:30:37.000Z","msg":"你架學神車應該有晒燈射落地下架喎"},{"pid":"741a94104b85142ded81f38d1be7d31ffe4cd104","tid":246303,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"學神睇尾轆棍仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525eca025ed4045a9efe2799d1577dc2f68fda2a","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師傅教<br />\n譬如你泊你右面s位<br />\n間車係個空位前面間車，你間車pat pat同佢pat pat成一直線<br />\n跟住扭盡右面，留位左鏡<br />\n當你左鏡睇到哂空位後面架車成個車頭，就回直架車<br />\n當架車左尾轆入左泊車個位後<br />\n向左扭盡，直至架車入哂個車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白 之後街泊一定參考各位既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c730d5cc039768d7e6081a40db034a7ad0779517","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你架學神車應該有晒燈射落地下架喎</blockquote><br />\n係有 係睇到位扭晒左軚 同臨尾扭晒右軚<br />\n係唔肯定中間扭正軚時話睇45度角<br />\n呢下唔關射燈事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadfdf3991f32583df085d70893a11182daf5e38","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學神睇尾轆棍仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n略有聽聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪左後窗口位睇雪糕筒上面碌棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37453e0db902fff7d071890f7d29bb233859da9","tid":246303,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師傅教<br />\n譬如你泊你右面s位<br />\n間車係個空位前面間車，<span style=\"color: red;\">你間車pat pat同佢pat pat成一直線</span><br />\n跟住扭盡右面，留位左鏡<br />\n當你左鏡睇到哂空位後面架車成個車頭，就回直架車<br />\n當架車左尾轆入左泊車個位後<br />\n向左扭盡，直至架車入哂個車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0035e3c0b4ad4fdc806322ad2305aba02e63367","tid":246303,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba150027c0b0da5f5a5d9381b502996f9909960","tid":246303,"uid":12683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  揸5.5頓泊S位1,2手就泊到 <br />\n但揸個fd架私家車就5,6手都泊唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n個人覺得私家車有頭 所以唔識預返個頭黎泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有後視會好啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0ed2ab6e7ba428fe5e0a745ab8b7f5c723cb18","tid":246303,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"個師傅教你S位泊車之前有冇整定雪糕筒、畫線同畫G字呀？<br />\n1. 入後波慢慢倒後望左鏡見到個地下橙色燈掂到條線就扭兩圈左軚<br />\n2. 望右鏡見到個G字就扭兩圈右軚<br />\n3. 最後都係望右鏡見到個地下橙色燈入咗白線就要扭盡右軚"},{"pid":"35f75fd756cecc3d5af9858c7d64df67bccf9ead","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個師傅教你S位泊車之前有冇整定雪糕筒、畫線同畫G字呀？<br />\n1. 入後波慢慢倒後望左鏡見到個地下橙色燈掂到條線就扭兩圈左軚<br />\n2. 望右鏡見到個G字就扭兩圈右軚<br />\n3. 最後都係望右鏡見到個地下橙色燈入咗白線就要扭盡右軚</blockquote><br />\n1同3一樣<br />\n2冇G字 只係叫我feel 45度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d87078fa7145dd6799d01c74d2036bc68bbd1c0","tid":246303,"uid":43607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"係美國揸左車6年,泊S位次數加埋10次都唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b840585ec5421cfed45480c24f63a44af537ef","tid":246303,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"加3度好過啦，45度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f5868c8f26f029800443f9341e60f1307f7ba6","tid":246303,"uid":8713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  揸5.5頓泊S位1,2手就泊到 <br />\n但揸個fd架私家車就5,6手都泊唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n個人覺得私家車有頭 所以唔識預返個頭黎泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有後視會好啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揸私家車有個車頭 硬係覺得個頭唔夠位入<br />\n要預勁多位先敢回軚"},{"pid":"3fd36c55d72875213bda73debc78cf5668c1251b","tid":246303,"uid":44815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"07956a1829b7af10c49a0cc4cde0cb4524f3faed","tid":246303,"uid":12683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  揸5.5頓泊S位1,2手就泊到 <br />\n但揸個fd架私家車就5,6手都泊唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n個人覺得私家車有頭 所以唔識預返個頭黎泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有後視會好啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揸私家車有個車頭 硬係覺得個頭唔夠位入<br />\n要預勁多位先敢回軚</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日驚唔夠位 個頭會hi到前車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83770b8d53301bc5f4f3a54d39b54c298470b85","tid":246303,"uid":116050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>揸開5.5頓車表示揸私家車唔識泊S位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  揸5.5頓泊S位1,2手就泊到 <br />\n但揸個fd架私家車就5,6手都泊唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n個人覺得私家車有頭 所以唔識預返個頭黎泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有後視會好啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揸私家車有個車頭 硬係覺得個頭唔夠位入<br />\n要預勁多位先敢回軚</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日驚唔夠位 個頭會hi到前車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架車入面睇好似就黎hi到，跟住要除安全帶，大半個身望出去睇，屌，原來距離前車仲有好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdc4cdfcbb7fc89a93dbc141c58dc9754339f32","tid":246303,"uid":47577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/225004_711d56a84b94630f4095c707d3e93373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F225004_711d56a84b94630f4095c707d3e93373.jpg&h=c0480fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享考車心法，唔知你明唔明"},{"pid":"112b8807c6a9836c7252fab4dcc85ba1024ca033","tid":246303,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/225004_711d56a84b94630f4095c707d3e93373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F225004_711d56a84b94630f4095c707d3e93373.jpg&h=c0480fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享考車心法，唔知你明唔明</blockquote><br />\n好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}